20
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:11,800
But it has its own rules.

21
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:44,520
It’s OK. I’ll stall them first.

22
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:49,550
You underestimate them.

23
00:02:49,550 --> 00:02:50,390
People from Dragon Sect

24
00:02:50,390 --> 00:02:52,550
all have good ears.

25
00:02:52,550 --> 00:02:53,720
It’s no different from speaking

26
