in front of them when you
talk so quietly.

27
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:58,720
I can hear everything you say.

28
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:00,440
You’re still alive?

29
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,450
We will give you to our master

30
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,000
to see how he will punish you.

31
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:08,270
Let’s deal with the two of them first.

32
00:03:08,670 --> 00:03:09,630
Wait.

33
00:03:09,630 --> 00:03:11,080
Have you considered it?

34
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,160
Are you really going to fight?

35
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,830
Why bother to consider?

36
00:03:13,830 --> 00:03:15,550
Think carefully.

37
00:03:15,550 --> 00:03:17,240
Don’t force me to use my dreadful move.

38
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,390
Dreadful move?

39
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:20,830
I’d like to know

40
00:03:20,830 --> 00:03:21,720
what it is.

41
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,360
Originally,

42
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,550
I was going to

43
00:03:25,550 --> 00:03:26,910
block this cave

44
00:03:26,910 --> 00:03:28,630
so you wouldn’t get yourselves killed.

45
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:29,960
But looks like

46
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,320
you are still looking for death.

47
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:34,030
I’ll just pull your tongue out

48
00:03:34,030 --> 00:03:35,600
to see if you dare to say that again!

49
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:38,440
You just know a formation.

50
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:40,880
Actually this formation

51
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,440
is easy to be broken.

52
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,800
This formation contains

53
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:47,670
the method of the five elements.

54
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:48,910
One of you beats the gong

55
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:50,440
to trigger the attack from the enemy

56
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:51,720
and show his weakness,

57
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:54,520
