58
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,440
The five of you guard each other

59
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:58,670
and exchange with other groups.

60
00:03:58,670 --> 00:04:01,440
So the changes will be endless.

61
00:04:01,830 --> 00:04:03,470
There are many people who know this.

62
00:04:03,910 --> 00:04:05,080
It’s no big deal!

63
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,550
But few of them

64
00:04:06,550 --> 00:04:07,750
