65
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:09,910
Weak point? How could you know?

66
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:12,240
It’s “Jin” on the position “Qian”.

67
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,630
If he is in danger,

68
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:15,320
