75
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:26,440
Mr. Yin,

76
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,550
it doesn’t matter if you are with us
or not.

77
00:04:28,550 --> 00:04:31,000
But now you have to stand on our side.

78
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,320
Think about it.

79
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:33,760
If we die,

80
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:35,230
