119
00:07:17,510 --> 00:07:20,040
Water Cutting?

120
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:26,740
At this time,

121
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:29,510
that old guy who can’t protect himself

122
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:31,640
