148
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:50,760
I thought he was invulnerable.

149
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,400
If not for his armor,

150
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:54,030
I would have already

151
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:55,470
taken his arms off.

152
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,470
