155
00:10:05,150 --> 00:10:06,350
Block the blade!

156
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:11,350
Lad.

157
00:10:11,350 --> 00:10:13,080
You have watched enough?

158
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:17,320
There was a craftsman

159
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:19,710
who was said to be able to
perform wonders

160
00:10:19,710 --> 00:10:21,650
and make many great weapons.

161
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:23,760
Other than that,

162
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,190
