285
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:55,620
Miss Zhou,

286
00:17:57,710 --> 00:17:59,710
before I die,

287
00:18:00,710 --> 00:18:02,580
I could have a fight with you

288
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:06,850
and teach you the Water Cutting.

289
00:18:08,350 --> 00:18:09,930
It already made me satisfied.

290
00:18:15,520 --> 00:18:19,560
I don’t care about North or South Blade.

291
00:18:19,560 --> 00:18:20,320
I remember

292
00:18:21,760 --> 00:18:24,050
Mr. Yin once told me…

293
00:18:25,230 --> 00:18:27,110
In the future,

294
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:29,900
you’ll have many difficulties to face.

295
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:32,310
I just don’t want

296
00:18:32,310 --> 00:18:34,160
you younger generation

297
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:36,350
to be destroyed in my hand.

298
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:46,560
Mr. Ji.

299
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:49,950
Pei,

300
00:18:52,190 --> 00:18:53,440
I’m sorry.

301
00:18:56,110 --> 00:18:57,360
This is all

302
00:18:59,470 --> 00:19:00,720
I can repay you.

303
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,280
Just go.

304
00:19:14,040 --> 00:19:15,700
Do we really have no way to help him?

305
00:19:31,780 --> 00:19:32,730
“Heaven.”

306
00:19:33,560 --> 00:19:35,760
“I have always been wanting”

307
00:19:35,760 --> 00:19:37,950
“to know you and cherish you.”

308
00:19:37,950 --> 00:19:39,680
“Only when the world comes to an end”

309
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,680
“can I throw away my love for you.”

310
00:19:43,430 --> 00:19:44,680
These scholars

311
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:48,000
always like to show off literary skills.

312
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,590
Not like me,

313
00:19:49,590 --> 00:19:51,000
who just want to start my own sect

314
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:53,640
after battling with all the masters.

315
00:19:58,190 --> 00:20:00,530
The first place in the world,

316
00:20:01,590 --> 00:20:04,070
or the good fame for half a life.

317
00:20:05,350 --> 00:20:06,900
Let all these things

318
00:20:09,520 --> 00:20:13,800
go with the wind...

319
00:20:55,310 --> 00:20:56,120
Mr. Yin.

320
00:20:59,310 --> 00:21:00,500
You killed Dragon Master,

321
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:02,470
and Mr. Ji is also dead.

322
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:04,250
You have got your revenge.

323
00:21:04,710 --> 00:21:06,190
How about his graciousness to you

324
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:07,890
for more than ten years?

325
00:21:08,560 --> 00:21:09,780
He has already died.

326
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:12,120
It’s just what he wanted.

327
00:21:18,760 --> 00:21:20,080
Are you also looking for
the Color of Ocean and Heaven?

328
00:21:23,190 --> 00:21:24,890
It’s none of your business

329
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:26,730
about what I’m going to do.

330
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:31,420
This belonged to my family.

331
00:21:32,310 --> 00:21:33,810
But Dragon Master once owned it.

332
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,470
So I won’t need it.

333
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,680
It’ll be yours.

334
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:39,200
If you don’t like it,

335
00:21:40,950 --> 00:21:42,190
you can just throw it.

336
00:21:42,190 --> 00:21:42,710
Mr. Yin!

337
00:21:42,710 --> 00:21:43,610
Chuchu,

338
00:21:44,430 --> 00:21:45,550
just keep it.

339
00:21:47,230 --> 00:21:48,830
It will be a dangerous journey.

340
00:21:48,830 --> 00:21:50,190
And you don’t know any martial art.

341
00:21:50,190 --> 00:21:52,640
It can save your life.

342
00:21:53,280 --> 00:21:54,400
Keep it.

343
00:22:09,100 --> 00:22:11,310
(Grave of Ji Yunchen)

344
00:22:11,310 --> 00:22:14,040
(Grave of Ji Yunchen)
A great master like Mr. Ji

345
00:22:14,040 --> 00:22:15,560
(Grave of Ji Yunchen)
could only hide his identity

346
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:17,470
(Grave of Ji Yunchen)
and be known by no other people.

347
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:19,230
(Grave of Ji Yunchen)
He shocked the world

348
00:22:19,230 --> 00:22:20,880
when first showed up.

349
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:24,070
Today I’m lucky to see the Water Cutting
come back to the world.

350
00:22:24,070 --> 00:22:26,190
I’ll always remember it.

351
00:22:26,760 --> 00:22:27,830
Mr. Ji said

352
00:22:27,830 --> 00:22:29,070
the Blade should be used to do things,

353
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:30,350
not to bring someone fame.

354
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:33,430
Here, I promise you that

355
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:35,590
the Water Cutting won’t be lost.

356
00:22:35,590 --> 00:22:38,710
I’ll live up to the blade in my hand.

357
00:22:39,710 --> 00:22:42,350
Back then, he was heroic and free.

358
00:22:42,350 --> 00:22:45,520
(Grave of Ji Yunchen)
But now, he is buried in a small tomb.

359
00:22:46,470 --> 00:22:47,520
Mr. Ji spent all his life

360
00:22:47,520 --> 00:22:49,160
to make up for this mistake.

361
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:50,430
No matter how,

362
00:22:50,430 --> 00:22:52,230
that’s all written off now.

363
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:54,110
I really admire

364
00:22:54,110 --> 00:22:56,160
your broad mind.

365
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:57,880
Hope in the next life

366
00:22:57,880 --> 00:23:00,310
you can achieve all your ambitions

367
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:01,880
and goals.

368
00:23:02,190 --> 00:23:04,040
Mr. Ji,

369
00:23:04,040 --> 00:23:05,110
we all know

370
00:23:05,110 --> 00:23:07,090
the one you cared the most is Yin Pei.

371
00:23:08,190 --> 00:23:09,830
Hope he can understand

372
00:23:09,830 --> 00:23:11,880
your good intention as soon as possible

373
00:23:11,880 --> 00:23:13,760
and come back to the right way,

374
00:23:13,760 --> 00:23:16,000
living up to the Yins’
chivalrous quality.

375
00:23:34,560 --> 00:23:36,070
Li Sheng,

376
00:23:36,070 --> 00:23:39,040
I’m curious about something.

377
00:23:39,040 --> 00:23:41,110
Why don’t you learn the
Snow-breaking Blade

378
00:23:41,110 --> 00:23:42,980
from your grandpa and father,

379
00:23:43,520 --> 00:23:45,470
but use Double Blades?

380
00:23:46,470 --> 00:23:48,040
Many schools are mixed together

381
00:23:48,040 --> 00:23:50,430
in the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

382
00:23:51,430 --> 00:23:52,560
When I was little,

383
00:23:52,950 --> 00:23:54,100
I liked to run around

384
00:23:54,470 --> 00:23:56,230
and liked everything I saw.

385
00:23:56,230 --> 00:23:58,230
Then I learned what I liked.

386
00:23:58,230 --> 00:23:59,950
Back then, I thought Double Blades

387
00:23:59,950 --> 00:24:02,560
might be stronger than a single blade
or sword.

388
00:24:02,950 --> 00:24:04,640
So I learned

389
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:06,620
the Double Blades from Xiaoxiang Sect.

390
00:24:07,590 --> 00:24:09,350
Later I wanted to learn the South Blade.

391
00:24:09,350 --> 00:24:10,310
But I didn’t

392
00:24:10,310 --> 00:24:12,370
know how to tell my aunt.

393
00:24:13,510 --> 00:24:15,340
That’s why my swordsmanship

394
00:24:15,520 --> 00:24:16,800
is not that great now.

395
00:24:19,310 --> 00:24:22,140
It’s rare for you to be introspective.

396
00:24:22,590 --> 00:24:23,550
Actually,

397
00:24:24,280 --> 00:24:27,160
it doesn’t matter whether it’s from

398
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:29,350
your ancestors or other sects.

399
00:24:29,350 --> 00:24:31,310
You’re Li Zheng’s grandson.

400
00:24:31,310 --> 00:24:33,920
But you don’t have to learn
the South Blade.

401
00:24:33,920 --> 00:24:35,710
If you’re the son of a fisherman,

402
00:24:35,710 --> 00:24:38,830
you don’t have to learn fishing.

403
00:24:38,830 --> 00:24:41,350
You should ask yourself

404
00:24:41,350 --> 00:24:43,590
about the truth inside this.

405
00:24:44,760 --> 00:24:47,000
I found that your swordsmanship

406
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:50,210
is kind of complicated and limited.

407
00:24:50,950 --> 00:24:53,760
That’s because you have too many
distracting thoughts.

408
00:24:53,760 --> 00:24:55,880
Especially while learning Double Blades,

409
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:59,320
you have to be more concentrated.

410
00:25:00,640 --> 00:25:02,120
Hope you can

411
00:25:02,830 --> 00:25:05,470
gradually learn the swordsmanship

412
00:25:05,470 --> 00:25:07,760
I taught you these days.

413
00:25:07,950 --> 00:25:10,400
You did teach me some formations.

414
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:12,430
When did you teach me swordsmanship?

415
00:25:14,160 --> 00:25:16,800
Everything in the world
is of the same method.

416
00:25:16,800 --> 00:25:20,190
Generally speaking, the formation
is the swordsmanship,

417
00:25:20,190 --> 00:25:22,430
and the swordsmanship is the formation.

418
00:25:22,430 --> 00:25:24,450
It depends on how you understand it.

419
00:25:26,470 --> 00:25:28,380
I’m leaving now.

420
00:25:28,710 --> 00:25:29,970
Take care.

421
00:25:31,470 --> 00:25:32,470
Sir,

422
00:25:32,470 --> 00:25:34,350
let me stay with you for some more days.

423
00:25:34,350 --> 00:25:36,430
Don’t bother.

424
00:25:36,920 --> 00:25:38,800
Then where are you going

425
00:25:38,800 --> 00:25:40,070
next?

426
00:25:42,430 --> 00:25:44,640
I’ll go travel around.

427
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:46,800
Since Qi School is gone,

428
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:49,490
I’ll be cosmopolitan.

429
00:26:12,590 --> 00:26:14,640
We have been walking for hours.

430
00:26:15,070 --> 00:26:17,520
It’s hard for Chuchu to come

431
00:26:17,520 --> 00:26:18,680
such a long way with us.

432
00:26:19,950 --> 00:26:21,000
Actually,

433
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:22,800
it’s even harder for you.

434
00:26:22,800 --> 00:26:23,920
After fighting with Dragon Master,

435
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,430
you can still walk such a long way.

436
00:26:25,430 --> 00:26:26,450
You are strong.

437
00:26:27,830 --> 00:26:29,570
Are you praising me or insulting me?

438
00:26:30,110 --> 00:26:31,710
Praising, of course.

439
00:26:33,920 --> 00:26:35,640
Looks like I have to practice more

440
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:37,350
on how to praise others.

441
00:26:37,350 --> 00:26:38,800
It depends on if Miss Zhou

442
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:40,680
will give me the chance.

443
00:26:41,680 --> 00:26:42,950
Yeah.

444
00:26:42,950 --> 00:26:44,640
I should give you an attack.

445
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:46,080
That’s too hard.

446
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:48,230
Fei…

447
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:52,880
There is a deserted house.

448
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:54,280
Let’s go have a rest there.

449
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:55,950
OK. I will go first

450
00:26:55,950 --> 00:26:57,210
to clean up the deserted inn.

451
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:03,630
Fei,

452
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:05,000
sorry.

453
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:06,490
Why?

454
00:27:07,430 --> 00:27:09,640
You and Xie are martial artists.

455
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:10,560
I walked so slow

456
00:27:10,560 --> 00:27:12,230
and held you back.

457
00:27:12,230 --> 00:27:14,160
That’s not like that.
Don’t think too much.

458
00:27:39,470 --> 00:27:41,950
Fei, what’s wrong?

459
00:27:41,950 --> 00:27:44,400
It’s OK. I have suppressed it.

460
00:27:45,560 --> 00:27:47,360
The Yellow and Green Spirit
caused trouble again?

461
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,690
Let me tell Xie.

462
00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:50,280
No. Don’t.

463
00:27:50,280 --> 00:27:51,430
It’s OK now.

464
00:27:51,430 --> 00:27:52,720
Don’t let him worry.

465
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:09,510
Ladies, welcome.

466
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:13,640
Good job.

467
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:14,800
Here, have a seat.

468
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:16,190
Master, have a seat.

469
00:28:16,190 --> 00:28:17,560
Move it backward a little bit.

470
00:28:17,560 --> 00:28:18,190
OK.

471
00:28:25,760 --> 00:28:26,830
Fei,

472
00:28:26,830 --> 00:28:28,470
if we meet a rival like Dragon Master
again,

473
00:28:28,470 --> 00:28:30,160
don’t act rashly.

474
00:28:30,560 --> 00:28:32,230
Then, should I be a coward like you?

475
00:28:33,800 --> 00:28:35,630
Turns out that I’m always a coward
in your mind.

476
00:28:38,430 --> 00:28:38,880
I…

477
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:43,230
Fei!

478
00:29:10,800 --> 00:29:13,780
“The old stones along the bridge
were covered with frost.”

479
00:29:15,070 --> 00:29:19,010
“A man who travels far from home
will never return.”

480
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,560
It’s your new work?

481
00:29:24,590 --> 00:29:25,800
New poem.

482
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:28,040
“Coward’s Forlornness”.

483
00:29:29,520 --> 00:29:30,860
It was a bad joke.

484
00:29:31,830 --> 00:29:32,870
You’re not a coward.

485
00:29:34,430 --> 00:29:35,280
Fei,

486
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:37,590
you knew you couldn’t beat
Dragon Master.

487
00:29:37,590 --> 00:29:40,000
Why did you promise Mr. Ji to do that?

488
00:29:42,830 --> 00:29:43,910
I just wonder

489
00:29:44,760 --> 00:29:47,110
why they could be so confidently

490
00:29:47,110 --> 00:29:48,620
and proudly evil.

491
00:29:49,110 --> 00:29:50,640
How can these villains

492
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:51,590
be so proud of

493
00:29:51,590 --> 00:29:52,520
the gross injustice they did

494
00:29:52,520 --> 00:29:54,400
more than 20 years ago

495
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:56,110
while the good guys

496
00:29:56,110 --> 00:29:57,970
were already buried in earth?

497
00:29:58,470 --> 00:29:59,470
They are just spoiled

498
00:29:59,470 --> 00:30:01,150
by the silence of many people.

499
00:30:08,830 --> 00:30:10,600
My new poem

500
00:30:11,040 --> 00:30:12,870
is a story about a deserter.

501
00:30:14,110 --> 00:30:15,680
What’s interesting about a deserter?

502
00:30:16,830 --> 00:30:18,190
What’s interesting about a hero?

503
00:30:18,190 --> 00:30:19,310
For the leisure time,

504
00:30:19,310 --> 00:30:21,190
why don’t we have some stories
about being a coward?

505
00:30:22,560 --> 00:30:24,160
Alright, alright.

506
00:30:24,160 --> 00:30:25,070
If there is a chance,

507
00:30:25,070 --> 00:30:26,830
I will tell the whole world

508
00:30:26,830 --> 00:30:28,400
with eagerness and zest

509
00:30:28,400 --> 00:30:30,350
that you, Xie Yun, are not a coward.

510
00:30:31,310 --> 00:30:32,420
Thank you then.

511
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:38,110
You can go on

512
00:30:38,110 --> 00:30:39,520
with your story about the deserter.

513
00:30:39,520 --> 00:30:41,680
I really want to listen to it.

514
00:30:46,070 --> 00:30:48,230
Before he became a deserter,

515
00:30:48,230 --> 00:30:50,690
he thought he was a great hero

516
00:30:51,590 --> 00:30:53,230
who could return home in honor

517
00:30:53,230 --> 00:30:55,500
and marry the girl he loved.

518
00:30:57,040 --> 00:30:58,640
But later he found

519
00:30:58,640 --> 00:31:00,430
that the government

520
00:31:00,430 --> 00:31:01,800
didn’t need him at all

521
00:31:03,040 --> 00:31:04,510
and even didn’t regard him as a human.

522
00:31:06,430 --> 00:31:08,730
He was just a living bait
to lure the enemy.

523
00:31:09,110 --> 00:31:10,560
His mission would be completed

524
00:31:10,560 --> 00:31:11,860
the moment when he died.

525
00:31:13,350 --> 00:31:14,180
So,

526
00:31:15,110 --> 00:31:16,020
he fled away.

527
00:32:23,560 --> 00:32:24,830
Anzhi,

528
00:32:24,830 --> 00:32:26,350
with all my life’s work,

529
00:32:26,350 --> 00:32:27,830
I temporarily shut

530
00:32:27,830 --> 00:32:29,880
-the poison in your veins.
-Uncle!

531
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:33,800
After that, you can no longer
use martial arts,

532
00:32:33,800 --> 00:32:36,680
but, live well on behalf of me.

533
00:32:43,040 --> 00:32:45,590
And then? What are you thinking about?

534
00:32:45,590 --> 00:32:47,190
What happened to that deserter?

535
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:48,770
Nothing.

536
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:51,920
But when the deserter returned home

537
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:52,830
after many difficulties,

538
00:32:52,830 --> 00:32:54,360
he didn’t find his girl.

539
00:32:55,070 --> 00:32:55,900
Why?

540
00:32:58,000 --> 00:33:00,000
Because that girl is a…

541
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:00,950
Weed Spirit.

542
00:33:00,950 --> 00:33:02,480
She had left riding a carp.

543
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:07,590
I… I have had enough rest.

544
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:09,560
I’ll go find some food there.

545
00:33:23,830 --> 00:33:24,920
Fei!

546
00:33:25,230 --> 00:33:26,280
Fei!

547
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:34,680
Oh, no. Her pulse condition is bad.

548
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:36,230
It must be because of the two spirits.

549
00:33:36,230 --> 00:33:37,760
What to do now?

550
00:33:37,760 --> 00:33:38,430
Hengyang.

551
00:33:38,430 --> 00:33:40,230
Someone in Hengyang can save her.

552
00:33:40,230 --> 00:33:40,830
But…

553
00:33:40,830 --> 00:33:42,760
But what? Go ahead.

554
00:33:42,760 --> 00:33:43,920
She is on the move.

555
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:45,680
I’m not sure if she is in the city.

556
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:47,200
We have to give it a try.

557
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:14,610
Who is it?

558
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:20,230
Fei, if you can hear me,

559
00:34:20,230 --> 00:34:21,630
do me a favor.

560
00:34:21,630 --> 00:34:23,690
We should escape now to save you.

561
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:24,790
Your Majesty?

562
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:26,710
Greeting, Your Majesty.

563
00:34:26,710 --> 00:34:27,900
General Feiqing?

564
00:34:30,600 --> 00:34:32,280
You’ve really kept a close following.

565
00:34:33,630 --> 00:34:34,410
Your Majesty,

566
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:36,120
I have asked the soldiers to go back.

