681
00:39:42,950 --> 00:39:45,670
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!

682
00:39:47,190 --> 00:39:49,080
Hyah! Hyah!

683
00:39:49,670 --> 00:39:51,320
Hyah! Hyah!

684
00:39:56,120 --> 00:39:56,630
Hyah!

