699
00:40:25,320 --> 00:40:27,000
Lord, if our time is limited,

700
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:29,230
I have an idea to save time.

701
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:30,800
Go ahead.

702
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:31,630
In the forest, there is

703
00:40:31,630 --> 00:40:33,710
